  <brief_title>Discontinuation of Dasatinib in Patients With Chronic Myeloid Leukemia-CP Who Have Maintained Complete Molecular Remission for Two Years; Dasatinib Stop Trial</brief_title>
  <official_title>Discontinuation of Dasatinib in Patients With Chronic Myeloid Leukemia in Chronic Phase Who Have Maintained Complete Molecular Remission for Two Years; Dasatinib Stop Trial</official_title>
