  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to assess whether dasatinib can be discontinued without
      occurrence of molecular relapse in patients with chronic myeloid leukemia in chronic phase in
      complete molecular remission (CMR) while on dasatinib.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
